### LHA Multi-Tenancy Complete Test Suite
@gatewayUrl = https://localhost:7100
@accountUrl = https://localhost:7150
@password = Admin@123456

# =========================================================================
# 1. HOST MANAGEMENT (Super Admin Actions)
# =========================================================================

### 1.1. Host Admin Login
# @name host_login
POST {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userNameOrEmail": "admin", 
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

@hostToken = {{host_login.response.body.result.data.accessToken}}

### 1.2. Query All Tenants (Host Side)
GET {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/tenants?PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{hostToken}}

###

# =========================================================================
# 2. TENANT REGISTRATION (Public/Host Side)
# =========================================================================

### 2.1. Register Per-Database Tenant
POST {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/auth/register-tenant
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tenantName": "tenant_per_db",
    "adminUserName": "admin_db",
    "adminEmail": "db@test.com",
    "adminPassword": "{{password}}",
    "databaseStyle": 2
}

###

### 2.2. Register Per-Schema Tenant
POST {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/auth/register-tenant
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tenantName": "tenant_per_schema",
    "adminUserName": "admin_schema",
    "adminEmail": "schema@test.com",
    "adminPassword": "{{password}}",
    "databaseStyle": 4
}

###

# =========================================================================
# 3. TENANT-SPECIFIC ACTIONS (Data Isolation Test)
# =========================================================================

### 3.1. Login to Per-Database Tenant (Subdomain)
# @name login_db
POST {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Host: tenant_per_db.localhost:7150

{
    "userNameOrEmail": "admin_db",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

@dbToken = {{login_db.response.body.result.data.accessToken}}

### 3.2. Query Users of Per-Database Tenant
GET {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/users?PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{dbToken}}
Host: tenant_per_db.localhost:7150

###

### 3.3. Query Users of Per-Schema Tenant
# Note: Usually you need to login to schema tenant first to get a token
# This is a sample query showing resolution
GET {{accountUrl}}/api/v1/identity/users?PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{dbToken}} 
Host: tenant_per_schema.localhost:7150